messages: Whose gonna pay attention, to your dreams, if you're not with me?
Keep me in the dark. Be kept in the dark.
Whose gonna pay attention, to your dreams, if you're not with me?
Keep me in the dark. Be kept in the dark.
Never let someone that hurt you back into your life, because it will happen again and again and hurts worse every time.
